org.cef.network

类 CefCookieManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.network.CefCookieManager

  • public abstract class CefCookieManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used for managing cookies. The methods of this class may be called on any thread unless otherwise indicated.
    用于管理cookie的类。除非另有说明，否则可以在任何线程上调用此类的方法。

    • 方法详细资料

      • createManager

        public static final CefCookieManager createManager(java.lang.String path,
                                                   boolean persistSessionCookies)
        Creates a new cookie manager. If |path| is empty data will be stored in memory only. Otherwise, data will be stored at the specified |path|. To persist session cookies (cookies without an expiry date or validity interval) set |persistSessionCookies| to true. Session cookies are generally intended to be transient and most Web browsers do not persist them.
        创建一个新的cookie管理器。如果|路径|空数据只会存储在内存中。否则，数据将存储在指定的| path |中。要保留会话cookie（没有过期日期或有效期间隔的cookie），请设置| persistSessionCookies |为真。会话cookie通常是暂时的，大多数Web浏览器不会持久化。
        返回:
        null if creation fails. 如果创建失败则为null。

      • deleteCookies

        public abstract boolean deleteCookies(java.lang.String url,
                                      java.lang.String cookieName)
        Delete all cookies that match the specified parameters. If both |url| and values |cookieName| are specified all host and domain cookies matching both will be deleted. If only |url| is specified all host cookies (but not domain cookies) irrespective of path will be deleted. If |url| is empty all cookies for all hosts and domains will be deleted. This method will be called on the IO thread. If posting the task was successful the method returns true.
        删除所有与指定参数匹配的cookie。如果两者都是| url |和值| cookieName |指定将删除所有匹配两者的主机和域cookie。如果只有| url |指定所有主机cookie（但不包括域cookie），不管路径将被删除。如果| url |为空是所有主机和域的所有cookie都将被删除。将在IO线程上调用此方法。如果发布任务成功，则该方法返回true。

      • flushStore

        public abstract boolean flushStore(CefCompletionCallback handler)
        Flush the backing store (if any) to disk and execute the specified |handler| on the IO thread when done. Returns false if cookies cannot be accessed.
        将后备存储（如果有）刷新到磁盘并执行指定的| handler |完成后在IO线程上。如果无法访问cookie，则返回false。

      • getGlobalManager

        public static final CefCookieManager getGlobalManager()
        Returns the global cookie manager. By default data will be stored at CefSettings.cache_path if specified or in memory otherwise.
        返回全局cookie管理器。默认情况下，如果指定，数据将存储在CefSettings.cache_path中，否则将存储在内存中。

      • setCookie

        public abstract boolean setCookie(java.lang.String url,
                                  CefCookie cookie)
        Sets a cookie given a valid URL and explicit user-provided cookie attributes. This function expects each attribute to be well-formed. It will check for disallowed characters (e.g. the ';' character is disallowed within the cookie value attribute). This method will be called on the IO thread. If posting the task was successful the method returns true.
        在给定有效URL和显式用户提供的cookie属性的情况下设置cookie。此函数期望每个属性都是格式良好的。它将检查不允许的字符（例如，cookie值属性中不允许使用';'字符）。将在IO线程上调用此方法。如果发布任务成功，则该方法返回true。

      • setStoragePath

        public abstract boolean setStoragePath(java.lang.String path,
                                       boolean persistSessionCookies)
        Sets the directory path that will be used for storing cookie data. If |path| is empty data will be stored in memory only. Otherwise, data will be stored at the specified |path|. To persist session cookies (cookies without an expiry date or validity interval) set |persistSessionCookies| to true. Session cookies are generally intended to be transient and most Web browsers do not persist them. Returns false if cookies cannot be accessed.
        设置将用于存储cookie数据的目录路径。如果|路径|空数据只会存储在内存中。否则，数据将存储在指定的| path |中。要保留会话cookie（没有过期日期或有效期间隔的cookie），请设置| persistSessionCookies |为真。会话cookie通常是暂时的，大多数Web浏览器不会持久化。如果无法访问cookie，则返回false。

      • setSupportedSchemes

        public abstract void setSupportedSchemes(java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> schemes)
        Set the schemes supported by this manager. By default only "http" and "https" schemes are supported. Must be called before any cookies are accessed.
        设置此经理支持的方案。默认情况下，仅支持“http”和“https”方案。必须在访问任何cookie之前调用。

      • visitAllCookies

        public abstract boolean visitAllCookies(CefCookieVisitor visitor)
        Visit all cookies. The returned cookies are ordered by longest path, then by earliest creation date. Returns false if cookies cannot be accessed.
        访问所有cookie。返回的cookie按最长路径排序，然后按最早创建日期排序。如果无法访问cookie，则返回false。

      • visitUrlCookies

        public abstract boolean visitUrlCookies(java.lang.String url,
                                        boolean includeHttpOnly,
                                        CefCookieVisitor visitor)
        Visit a subset of cookies. The results are filtered by the given url scheme, host, domain and path. If |includeHttpOnly| is true HTTP-only cookies will also be included in the results. The returned cookies are ordered by longest path, then by earliest creation date. Returns false if cookies cannot be accessed.
        访问一部分Cookie。结果通过给定的url方案，主机，域和路径进行过滤。如果| includeHttpOnly |是真的只有HTTP的cookie也将包含在结果中。返回的cookie按最长路径排序，然后按最早创建日期排序。如果无法访问cookie，则返回false。
